CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. B10 reads: "Chi Delta Mu Fraternity Entertains Lavishly - Dr. Oswald Nickens, third from left; Mrs. Nickens, far right, and guests." Portion of accompanying article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 20, 1960, pg. A7 by Toki Schalk Johnson reads:"Wednesday brought forth the annual dinner dance given by the Chi Delta Mu Fraternity in beautifully decorated New Arena."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four men, including Dr. Oswald Nickens, third from left, and four women, including Mrs. Nickens, far right, seated at rectangular banquet table for Chi Delta Mu dinner dance in New Arena Supper Club
